{
  "name": "Overload Magic",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-life-soul-green.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p class=\"pf0\"><span class=\"cf1\">You can spend <strong>1 AP + 1 MP</strong> in Combat to channel</span><span class=\"cf0\"> </span><span class=\"cf1\">raw magical energy for 1 minute, or until you become</span><span class=\"cf0\"> </span><span class=\"cf1\">Incapacitated, die, or choose to end it early at any time for</span><span class=\"cf0\"> </span><span class=\"cf1\">free.</span></p><p class=\"pf0\"><span class=\"cf1\">For the duration, your magic is overloaded and you’re</span><span class=\"cf0\"> </span><span class=\"cf1\">subjected to the following effects:</span></p><ul><li>You gain +5 to all Spell Attacks and Spell Checks you make.</li><li><p>You must immediately make an <strong>Attribute</strong> <strong>Save</strong> (your choice) against your <strong>Save</strong> <strong>DC</strong> upon using this Feature, and again at the start of each of your turns. <br><strong>Failure:</strong> You gain <strong>Exhaustion</strong>. You lose any Exhaustion gained in this way when you complete a <strong>Short</strong> <strong>Rest</strong>.</p></li></ul>",
